# Platform 3.0 App Templates

**UNIVERSAL CRITICAL ENFORCEMENT - NO EXCEPTIONS - NO CONTRADICTIONS:**

### ‚ùå NEVER Generate These (Immediate Rejection)
- ‚ùå `"whitelisted-domains"` - Platform 2.3 syntax, deprecated and invalid in 3.0
- ‚ùå `"product"` structure - Use `"modules"` in Platform 3.0
- ‚ùå Plain HTML: `<button>`, `<input>`, `<select>`, `<textarea>` - Use Crayons ONLY
- ‚ùå `{{variable}}` syntax - Causes FQDN validation errors
- ‚ùå Host with path: `api.example.com/api` - MUST be FQDN only
- ‚ùå Host with encoded chars: `%7B%7Bvar%7D%7D.example.com` - Invalid
- ‚ùå Path without `/`: `api/endpoint` - MUST start with `/`
- ‚ùå App files in workspace root - MUST create new app folder
- ‚ùå Frontend app without `icon.svg` - #1 validation failure cause
- ‚ùå OAuth credentials in `iparams.json` - MUST be in `oauth_iparams`

### ‚úÖ ALWAYS Generate These (Mandatory)
- ‚úÖ **`app/styles/images/icon.svg`** - MUST EXIST for frontend apps - NO EXCEPTIONS
- ‚úÖ **FQDN only hosts** - `api.example.com` (no path, no encoded characters)
- ‚úÖ **Paths start with `/`** - `/api/v2/endpoint`
- ‚úÖ **`<%= context.variable %>`** - For iparams in request templates
- ‚úÖ **`<%= iparam.name %>`** - For app-specific iparams
- ‚úÖ **`<%= access_token %>`** - For OAuth authorization
- ‚úÖ **`"modules"` structure** - NOT `"product"`
- ‚úÖ **`"engines"` block** - node and fdk versions
- ‚úÖ **Crayons components** - fw-button, fw-input, fw-select, fw-textarea, etc.
- ‚úÖ **Crayons CDN in ALL HTML** - BOTH script tags (ESM and nomodule)
- ‚úÖ **New app folder** - e.g., `my-app/` in parent directory
- ‚úÖ **`oauth_iparams` in `oauth_config.json`** - NOT in regular iparams.json
- ‚úÖ **At least one product module** - Even if empty `{}`

